	<id>dev.boxxy.BoxxyTerminal</id>
	<name>Boxxy Terminal</name>
	<developer id="io.github.boxxy-dev">
    	<name>Boxxy Dev</name>
    </developer>

	<summary>The Stupid Linux Terminal</summary>
	<description>
	    <p>A Terminal written in GTK and Rust that integrates a blazing fast Claw-like AI!</p>
	    <p>Features:</p>
	    <ul>
	    <li>Split panes with soft swap</li>
	    <li>Preview videos via GTK widget</li>
	    <li>Kitty Graphics Protocol support</li>
	    <li>Self improving AI with local models and memories 🦀</li>
	    <li>Headless modern terminal in pure Rust</li>
	    <li>And a few more..</li>
	    </ul>
	    <p>NOTE: Boxxy is in preview. Short term memories database might get wiped, since Boxxy doesn't support migrations yet</p>
	</description>

